    "description": "IMURA & Co.,Ltd. engages in the manufacture and sale of paper and other products in Japan. The company operates through Package Solutions, and Mailing Services segments. It offers paper products, such as envelopes, bags made from nonwoven fabrics and films, and stationery. The company is also involved in the planning and production of print and direct mail; and provision, enclosing of sealing products, shipping, storage, and information processing businesses. In addition, it engages in the advertising agency business; sale of computers and peripheral equipment; and development and production of software, production, sales and maintenance management, as well as provides inkjet printing services. The company was formerly known as Imura Envelope Co., Inc. and changed its name to IMURA & Co.,Ltd. in February 2023. IMURA & Co.,Ltd. was founded in 1918 and is headquartered in Osaka, Japan."
